# Code owners for miasma-detect.
# Syntax: <path pattern>  <owner(s)>
# The last matching pattern wins. Owners are auto-requested for review on PRs
# touching matching files (enforced only if "Require review from Code Owners"
# is enabled in the branch ruleset).

# Default owner for everything.
* @amfred

# Security-sensitive surfaces — keep an explicit owner even as the list grows.
/src/            @amfred
/action.yml      @amfred
/.github/        @amfred
/SECURITY.md     @amfred
